  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Aviation Minister welcomes new investment to improve passenger experience at Leeds Bradford Airport
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  
  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Minister sees construction begin on a major extension at Leeds Bradford Airport. 
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

